  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaiten is a roguelike tactical-strategy game. Spin the wheel with various move opportunities and develop your strategy based on the results. Build your deck with special perk cards purchased from the shop between sessions and empower your pawns! Achieve victory to unlock new rage abilities and opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your pawns are your warriors on this battlefield, but they are only as strong as the perks you equip them with. Create a collection of powerful perk cards and devise devastating combinations that can change the course of battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/4905eb544f3228b063ab9dd06b21386c.avif?t=1746032451\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras_big/4905eb544f3228b063ab9dd06b21386c.avif?t=1746032451 width=800 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPIN THE WHEEL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each turn begins with the spinning of the wheel that determines your move. Will you land on a devastating attack, a powerful item, or a special move that will change the course of the game?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMMAND YOUR PAWNS </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your pawn lineup in tactical combat. Each pawn can attack the enemy across from it, but choose your targets wisely - your decisions could make the difference between victory and defeat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR DECK!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each perk grants your pawns unique abilities and bonuses. Increase your defensive, offensive, or economic power. Grow stronger and win the battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WIN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win 3 out of 5 sessions to emerge victorious! But remember! If all your pawns die, you lose completely.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaiten is a roguelike tactical-strategy game. Spin the wheel with various move opportunities and develop your strategy based on the results. Build your deck with special perk cards purchased from the shop between sessions and empower your pawns! Achieve victory to unlock new rage abilities and opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/db46d5803b64b18fc139e8439f4be587.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your pawns are your warriors on this battlefield, but they are only as strong as the perks you equip them with. Create a collection of powerful perk cards and devise devastating combinations that can change the course of battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/4905eb544f3228b063ab9dd06b21386c.avif?t=1746032451\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras_big/4905eb544f3228b063ab9dd06b21386c.avif?t=1746032451 width=800 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPIN THE WHEEL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each turn begins with the spinning of the wheel that determines your move. Will you land on a devastating attack, a powerful item, or a special move that will change the course of the game?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMMAND YOUR PAWNS </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your pawn lineup in tactical combat. Each pawn can attack the enemy across from it, but choose your targets wisely - your decisions could make the difference between victory and defeat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/9557e4a7426caefd226ca66ff1c7582a.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR DECK!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each perk grants your pawns unique abilities and bonuses. Increase your defensive, offensive, or economic power. Grow stronger and win the battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.poster.avif?t=1746032451\" width=800 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.webm?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3464540/extras/5e6eb5a6bec0413f6535b7befa2808fd.mp4?t=1746032451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WIN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win 3 out of 5 sessions to emerge victorious! But remember! If all your pawns die, you lose completely.</p>",
